1 CONT Dom^a Sexag^ma Pmissis tribus ex more R. D. Christophorus Popel astitit Mat^o contracto inter Georgium, filium q. Leonardi Harish, et Helena coni: una cum Ursula, filia q. Se, bastiani Markustizh, et Dorothea coni: utriq ex Olshenik; ibiq et in missa nupt^i bndixit pntibus Michaele Saionez et Posnuez..
1 CONT
1 CONT Sexagesima Sunday. Three banns having been published according to custom, Rev. Fr. Christophorus Popel assisted at the marriage contracted between Georgius, son of the late Leonardus Harish and his wife Helena; together with Ursula, daughter of the late Sebastianus Markustizh and his wife Dorothea; both from Olshenik; and there, also in the nuptial mass, he gave the blessing, in the presence of Michael Saionez and Posnuez..
